<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>   
    <title>Paints</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Learn more about our painted cabinets, and the range of colors available.">
    <style>
        .hero{
            background-image: url(/images/imagery/DSC_0081.JPG);
        }
        .content{
            padding-left: 50px;
        }
        .text-image-container {
            display: flex; /* For side-by-side on larger screens */
            align-items: flex-start; /* Align items to the top */
        }
        .text-column {
            width: 60%;
            padding-right: 20px; /* Add some spacing between text and image */
        }
        .image-column {
            width: 40%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Media query for mobile devices (adjust max-width as needed) */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .text-image-container {
                flex-direction: column; /* Stack items vertically */
            }
            .text-column {
                width: 100%;
                padding-right: 0; /* Remove right padding on mobile */
                margin-bottom: 20px; /* Add spacing below text */
            }
            .image-column {
                width: 100%;
            }
            .content {
                padding-left: 20px; /* Adjust padding for mobile */
                padding-right: 20px; /* Add right padding for mobile */
            }
            .content table {
                display: block; /* Make the table behave like a block */
            }
            .content tr {
                display: block; /* Make table rows behave like blocks */
            }
            .content td {
                display: block; /* Make table data cells behave like blocks */
                width: 100%; /* Take full width */
                text-align: left; /* Align text to the left on mobile */
            }
            .content td:last-child {
                text-align: center; /* Center the image in the second (image) 'td' */
            }
            .content td img {
                width: 80%; /* Adjust image width for mobile */
                max-width: 300px; /* Optional: set a maximum width for the image */
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="hero">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <div class="highlight">
        <h1>Paint</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="text-image-container">
            <div class="text-column">
                <h2>Painted Cabinets</h2>
                <p>
                    Painted cabinets offer a lot of flexibility in design. You can choose any color to match your style or needs, whether you want a classic look or something more unique. Custom-painted cabinets give you the freedom to create a look that works best for your project.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We can match any color from popular fan decks or color indexes to make sure your cabinets are the exact shade you're looking for.
                </p>

                <h3>A Range of Color Choices</h3>
                <p>
                    With painted cabinets, the options are nearly endless. You can choose a color that fits your vision, whether it's something simple or bold. If you need a specific color to match other elements in your space, we can do that too.
                </p>

                <h3>Durability and Finish</h3>
                <p>
                    Our painted finishes are smooth and even, providing a lasting look that’s easy to maintain. These cabinets are built to stand up to everyday use while still looking good over time.
                </p>

                <h3>Your Cabinets, Your Color</h3>
                <p>
                    With painted cabinets, the choice is entirely up to you. Whether you're looking for a classic or a custom color, we’ll help you achieve the perfect look.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="image-column">
                <img src="/images/imagery/IMG_1737.jpg" alt="Painted cabinet samples" style="width:60%;">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>